data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!!! THIS 3 BEDROOM 2 BATH COUNTRY HOME SITS ON 2.58 ACRES OF LAND WITH A 36X56 EVENT BARN AND A 20X30 BOATHOUSE. THE EVENT BARN CAN BE ANOTHER PASSIVE INCOME AS THIS CAN HOST PARTIES, WEDDINGS, ANNIVERSARIES AND MUCH MORE. OUTSIDE OF THE EVENT BARN IS A NICE BIG 10X20 HIS AND HER AIR CONDITIONER BATHROOMS AND PLENTY OF ROOM FOR PARKING. THIS HOME FEATURES AN ABOVE GROUND 15 FT POOL,  A 12X26 SCREENED IN BACK PATIO. GRANITE COUNTERTOPS IN THE KITCHEN AND BATHROOMS. THE ENTIRE HOME HAS BEAUTIFUL UPDATED CERAMIC TILE FLOORING. THE KITCHEN FEATURES A 3X6 ISLAND WITH DRAWERS AND CUSTOM WOOD SOFT CLOSE CABINETS. IN 2018 THE DOORS, WINDOWS (grade below hurricane proof) PLUMBING, HOT WATER HEATER, 3D SHINGLES, WERE REPLACED. THE BOATHOUSE HAS ROLL UP DOORS ON EACH END FOR EASY ACCESS TO PULL STRAIGHT IN WITH YOUR BOAT, 4 WHEELER, LAWN TRAILER ETC....CALL FOR A SHOWING TODAY!
